The pod slowly opened, revealing a sleeping female transformer. She blinked 
her eyes and slowly sat up, rubbing her head. The landing had been rough, 
and she had a killer headache. She didn't remember anything but that her 
name was Cepta.

Cepta saw Wildrider and Dead-End while turning her head. Her eyes looked at 
the weapons and widened.

"Hello..." She said carefully. She didn't wanna be hurt, so she tried her 
best to be non-threatening.
